{"body": "Adding methods to the API doesn't count as a change. \n\nListing a method as a fix for a deprecated method, KNOWING it's going to be deprecated itself isn't fair to you, and it's certainly not fair to developers. Figure out what the final resting place for this functionality is (it sounds like it's update_columns), and get it into every version possible so that people can adopt it ASAP. ", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7267925", "created_at": "2012-07-26T02:39:12Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7159#issuecomment-7267925", "updated_at": "2012-07-26T02:39:12Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7159, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/GeekOnCoffee", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0bc875c603399dbfb1f166548c64dd76?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F0836cd30df8e8f76a7dd3124c0ee4550.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0bc875c603399dbfb1f166548c64dd76", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "GeekOnCoffee", "type": "User", "id": 240650, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/GeekOnCoffee/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ff5fbd3543c15100be02"}, "id": 7267925, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7159"}
